{"article_id":"j2MgcIhuCDnGew7t","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Taliban have released a video","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"showing the handover of Sgt . Bowe Bergdahl into U.S. custody over the weekend .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"The video was emailed to media outlets Wednesday .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Pentagon spokesman Rear Adm. John Kirby said","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"that the Defense Department was reviewing the video ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"but had `` no reason","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"to doubt [ its ] authenticity . ''","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"`` Regardless , ''","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Rear Adm. Kirby said ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"`` we know","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"the transfer was peaceful and successful ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"and our focus remains on getting Sgt . Bergdahl the care","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"he needs . ''","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"The video opens","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"by showing Bergdahl in traditional Afghan clothing","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"sitting in a white pickup truck","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"parked on a hillside somewhere in eastern Afghanistan .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"More than a dozen Taliban fighters with machine guns stand around the truck and on the hillside .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Bergdahl ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"who is clean shaven and has a shaved head in the video ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"is seen blinking frequently","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"as he looks at and listens to his captors .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"The video is narrated by a Taliban militant ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"who at one point says ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"`` We told them","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"there are 18 armed fighters","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"and the Americans said","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"that 's all right . ''","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"A Black Hawk helicopter then lands","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"and two Taliban fighters ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"one","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"carrying a white flag ,","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"lead Bergdahl half way .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"He is greeted and taken by three Western-looking men in civilian clothing to the helicopter ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"where soldiers in Army uniforms are waiting .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"According to the video 's narrator ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"the handover took place around 4 p.m. Saturday in the area of Bati in Ali Sher district of eastern Khost province .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"As the helicopter approaches ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"one of the Taliban men gets closer to Bergdahl","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"and is heard speaking in Pashto , one of two main Afghan languages .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"`` Do n't come back to Afghanistan , ''","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"the man tells Bergdahl .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"`` You wo n't make it out alive next time , ''","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"he adds","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"as some of the others are heard laughing .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"Just before the helicopter lands ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"a group of Taliban near the pickup shout :","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"`` Long life to Mujahedeen , ''","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"or holy warriors","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"as the Taliban call themselves .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"A Taliban statement ,","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"also distributed to media ,","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"quoted their leader Mullah Mohammad Omar","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"describing the release of the five Taliban officials from Guantanamo as a significant achievement for the movement .","depth":4},{"id":54,"text":"As the video shows the helicopter taking off ,","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"the message `` Don ' [ sic ] come back to Afghanistan '' pops up on the screen .","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"The video also showed the arrival in Qatar of the five Taliban militants","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"released from Guantanamo Bay in exchange for Bergdahl 's freedom .","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"The video shows the men being greeted with embraces","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"as a Taliban song plays in the background .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"The aftermath of Bergdahl 's release has been consumed by controversy ,","depth":3},{"id":61,"text":"with many service members claiming","depth":4},{"id":62,"text":"that Bergdahl deserted prior to his capture in 2009 .","depth":4},{"id":63,"text":"Members of Congress have alleged","depth":3},{"id":64,"text":"that the administration broke the law","depth":4},{"id":65,"text":"by not giving them 30 days notice of the impending release of the militants from Guantanamo Bay .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":131,"left":125,"right":130,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":115,"right":124,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":115,"left":78,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":68,"right":77,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":67,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":71,"right":76,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":3,"right":70,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":70,"left":4,"right":69,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":69,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":72,"right":75,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":72,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":73,"right":74,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":73,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":86,"right":113,"relation":"elabora